<br>
I must say, I am quite impressed with the graphics of this game. Quite visual for a MMORPG. But then again.. EQ's graphics are sub-standard compared to most modern games. <br>
<br>
I started a Terran Trader. I have enough of a hard time making money on EQ, I don't want that same problem with this one! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I made it to 8th level, mostly by exploring all the nav points in the various earth systems. As a trader, I do spend most of my time exploring.. but.. oh well. I'm not concerned. I have to get to the Vega system, somehow.. from the Earth System. Can you say, Mission Impossible? hehe<br>
<br>
All in all, I fell for this game hard last night. A must pickup, if you are into the space flight! 2 Daggers up!<br>
